    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. The engine requires significant work to be road-worthy, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows heavy wear, including several dents and areas of rust, while the interior has sustained considerable damage over the years. This is not a daily driver and will likely need to be towed from the lot, but it offers potential for someone with the right tools and time.",
      "price": 6500.0,
